"title": "7032: unity, of God's people",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7032: unity, of god's people",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A distinguishing characteristic of God's people, which derives from their common relationship with God, and is expressed in commitment to one another, mutual concern, concerted action and harmony within the believing community.</p>\n<h2>Unity in a common relationship with God</h2>\n<h3>As children of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:10\">MAL 2:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps133:1\">PSA 133:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:8-Matt23:9\">MAT 23:8–23:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:15-Rom8:17\">ROM 8:15–8:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:2\">COL 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:12\">COL 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:1\">1JN 5:1</a></p>\n<h3>As the people of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9-1Pet2:10\">1PE 2:9–2:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:7\">EXO 6:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:5-Exod19:6\">EXO 19:5–19:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:6\">DEU 7:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:24\">2SA 7:24</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:22\">1CH 17:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:17\">MAL 3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:14\">EPH 1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:25\">HEB 11:25</a></p>\n<h2>Unity in a common union with Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:16-1Cor10:17\">1CO 10:16–10:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:27\">1CO 12:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:52\">JHN 11:52</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:4-Rom12:5\">ROM 12:4–12:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:12\">1CO 12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:26-Gal3:28\">GAL 3:26–3:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:17-Eph2:19\">EPH 2:17–2:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:16\">EPH 4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:11\">COL 3:11</a></p>\n<h2>Unity through common receiving of the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:13\">1CO 12:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa34:16\">ISA 34:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:45-Acts10:47\">ACT 10:45–10:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:4-1Cor12:11\">1CO 12:4–12:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:14\">2CO 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:22\">EPH 2:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:4\">HEB 6:4</a></p>\n<h2>Unity in a common faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:4-Eph4:6\">EPH 4:4–4:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:13\">EPH 4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:4\">TIT 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:1-1John1:3\">1JN 1:1–1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:3\">JUD 1:3</a></p>\n<h2>Expressions of unity among God's people</h2>\n<h3>Commitment to one another</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:1-1Sam18:4\">1SA 18:1–18:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:16-Ruth1:17\">RUT 1:16–1:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:8\">1TH 2:8</a></p>\n<h3>Sharing possessions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:32\">ACT 4:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:11\">LUK 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:44-Acts2:45\">ACT 2:44–2:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:13\">ROM 12:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:27\">ROM 15:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:6\">GAL 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:6\">2TI 2:6</a></p>\n<h3>Giving support</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:3\">JOS 22:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut3:18\">DEU 3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:24-Heb10:25\">HEB 10:24–10:25</a></p>\n<h3>Sharing troubles</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:7\">2CO 1:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:14\">PHP 4:14</a></p>\n<h2>Unity expressed in agreement with one another</h2>\n<h3>Living in harmony</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps133:1\">PSA 133:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:3\">EPH 4:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:8\">1PE 3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:16\">ROM 12:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:17\">ROM 14:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:24\">1CO 10:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:25\">EPH 4:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:2\">PHP 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:12-Col1:14\">COL 1:12–1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:15\">COL 3:15</a></p>\n<h3>United in purpose</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:27\">PHP 1:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg20:11\">JDG 20:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam14:7\">1SA 14:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:8-Ezra3:10\">EZR 3:8–3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:6\">NEH 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:19-Matt18:20\">MAT 18:19–18:20</a></p>\n<h3>Of one mind</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:10\">1CO 1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:12\">2CH 30:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:2\">PHP 2:2</a></p>\n<h2>Unity expressed in worshipping together</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:5-Rom15:6\">ROM 15:5–15:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:22\">PSA 22:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:26\">PSA 68:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps122:1\">PSA 122:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:26\">1CO 14:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:12\">HEB 2:12</a></p>\n<h2>Unity marks out God's people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:21-John17:23\">JHN 17:21–17:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:34-John13:35\">JHN 13:34–13:35</a></p>",
